Daryl Sabara https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daryl_Sabara 0 Daryl Christopher Sabara (born June 14, 1992) is an American actor, perhaps best known for playing Juni Cortez in the Spy Kids film series, as well as for a variety of television and film appearances, including Generator Rex, Wizards of Waverly Place, Father of the Pride, The Polar Express, Keeping Up with the Steins, Halloween, World's Greatest Dad, Grimm, and America's Most Talented Kids (on which he was a judge).
